<i>Calling family link.</i>

54:11.745 --> 54:13.847
Danny, have you seen
the news over here?

54:13.872 --> 54:16.324
Your favourite
woman Prime Minister!

54:16.349 --> 54:17.628
I've actually met her.

54:17.690 --> 54:21.697
I love it, she's a nightmare,
the whole system's in pieces.

54:21.722 --> 54:24.558
Oh, Dan, mate, no,
take me off the family link.

54:25.140 --> 54:26.206
We've got to catch up.

54:26.231 --> 54:28.157
A lot of things have
changed since you went away.

54:28.352 --> 54:29.402
<i>Sorry, Celeste.</i>

54:29.427 --> 54:31.738
I don't mind. It doesn't
bother me, you stay on the link.

54:32.347 --> 54:34.635
Just do what you want.
You're very fond of saying

54:34.660 --> 54:35.832
it's your family.

54:35.857 --> 54:36.989
<i>Don't start.</i>

54:37.059 --> 54:38.598
Excuse me!

54:38.895 --> 54:42.729
I think, if anyone started
this, it was you, Stephen.

54:42.754 --> 54:45.520
Can I just point out... Daniel
left his husband for someone else,

54:45.545 --> 54:46.871
<i>no-one had a go at him.</i>

54:46.896 --> 54:48.418
<i>Me, it's the end of the world.</i>

54:48.747 --> 54:49.808
<i>Why is that?</i>

54:50.168 --> 54:51.406
I thought I'd better say.

54:51.582 --> 54:55.012
Oh, Viktor, sorry, are you okay?

54:55.094 --> 54:56.628
Hello! Where are you?

54:56.653 --> 54:58.724
Oh, Vik, mate, do us
a favour put Daniel on.

54:58.951 --> 54:59.951
It's a long story.

55:00.008 --> 55:01.763
Wait, sorry, but it
says you're home.

55:02.318 --> 55:04.155
You're phoning from Uncle
Dan's. You're in Britain?

55:04.179 --> 55:05.982
Oh, my God, no way!

55:06.007 --> 55:07.035
You did it.

55:07.204 --> 55:08.220
How did that happen?

55:08.245 --> 55:10.060
<i>Oh, that's brilliant!</i>

55:10.085 --> 55:11.958
That's amazing! How
did you do it, Dan?

55:14.111 --> 55:15.677
Danny, are you there?

55:17.942 --> 55:19.880
I'm at the house
and Daniel's dead.

55:22.412 --> 55:23.872
<i>I'm sorry, but he drowned.</i>

55:25.864 --> 55:27.655
<i>We thought we could
get across the Channel,</i>

55:28.584 --> 55:30.826
<i>but on the news
it says 17 bodies...</i>

55:32.229 --> 55:33.295
<i>that was Daniel.</i>

55:34.226 --> 55:35.226
He's dead.

55:35.924 --> 55:36.928
<i>He drowned.</i>

55:38.326 --> 55:42.282
We got half a mile from the
shore, but that's a very long way.

55:44.237 --> 55:45.401
- What?
- <i>The police don't know.</i>

55:45.425 --> 55:48.185
<i>His passport was gone,
his wallet was in his bag,</i>

55:48.210 --> 55:49.404
<i>and his bag was lost.</i>

55:50.535 --> 55:55.092
<i>So, he's in a town on the
coast called Rye, unidentified.</i>

55:56.390 --> 55:57.545
<i>I didn't want to do that.</i>

55:59.483 --> 56:03.463
But I thought, if I came
here, they'd never find me.

56:06.320 --> 56:07.826
That doesn't work, I know.

56:10.221 --> 56:14.481
I apologise to you all,
but we got on the boat,

56:14.956 --> 56:16.090
and the boat sank.

56:17.163 --> 56:18.286
And he's dead.

56:21.907 --> 56:23.068
I came home.

56:24.646 --> 56:25.646
Is this home?

57:09.934 --> 57:10.938
Okay.

57:41.446 --> 57:43.376
Viktor, please, are you there?

57:44.970 --> 57:45.970
Viktor!

57:47.200 --> 57:48.376
Viktor?

57:48.476 --> 57:50.266
Open the door!

57:51.774 --> 57:52.915
Viktor!

57:54.206 --> 57:55.262
Viktor!
